(Can we please get Terrosaur on-line?)


Quickstrike:





Quickstrike woke up. He felt a heavyness on his tail, weighing it down. He 
bobbed it and looked over. The first thing that he saw Stingtra. Thank 
Primus she followed orders. The other thing that he saw was a blanket over 
his legs.

He stood up, and went to take it off, but his claws wouldn't reach. He tried 
left, then right. He tried to throw it off with his tail, hoping that it 
would slide off, but it didn't. What did she do, staple it on?

"Get this thing off," he quietly said.
